&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-getting-started-with-hugo&#34;&gt;ðŸš€ &lt;strong&gt;Getting Started with Hugo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hugo makes it easy to build a lightning-fast website with minimal setup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-install-hugo&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Install Hugo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First, you&amp;rsquo;ll need to install Hugo on your system:&lt;/p&gt;
